title: Wilkes-Barre Dog Training Club Holds Puppy Graduation
title_page: Wilkes-Barre Dog Training Club Holds Puppy Graduation
maintext: A puppy class graduation was held recently at the Wilkes-Barre Dog Training Club, Hanover Twp. From left, are Julia Chmielowski with her dog, Lily, and Jean Schappert with her dog, Lexie. Class Instructor was Linda Harris. The dog owners and their companions enjoyed learning the basic commands for having a well mannered family pet. The club is located at R320 Lee Park Ave., Hanover Twp., and meets the third Wednesday of every month. Public is welcome. For information, call 570-829-8430.
